prompts.frontCover: Flat 2D illustration of a humorous royal scene in a clean minimalist style, featuring the people from the reference photo as cartoon characters. The person on the left, Lao Lao, is depicted as a queen sitting comically on a simple, elegant throne. She wears a small, crooked gold crown and has a pampered, content expression. The person on the right, Jordan, is dressed as a royal guard in a simple uniform with a funny, oversized furry hat. He is kneeling beside the throne, diligently feeding the queen a single green grape from a bunch, while also fanning her with a giant, stylized tropical leaf. The entire scene is set against a solid, soft pastel background. In the center, below the characters, is the text "Happy Birthday, your majesty" in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script. The artwork uses simple shapes, clean lines, and a limited color palette for a modern, humorous effect.
